title: ‘Survivor’ Season 42, Episode 10 With Ben 'Coach' Wade
description:
Tyson and Riley are joined by 'Survivor: Tocantins,' 'Survivor: Heroes vs. Villains,' and 'Survivor: South Pacific' contestant Ben "Coach" Wade. They discuss the Do or Die challenge, where Drea went wrong, and how people react to getting voted off. Plus, did Omar finally make a mistake?
Hosts: Tyson Apostol and Riley McAtee
Guest: Ben Wade
Associate Producer: Carlos Chiriboga
